Package: ggsano
Title: Create elegant figures and documents accoring to Sciensano standards
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Robby",
           family = "De Pauw",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "robby.depauw@sciensano.be",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4242-9062"))
Description: ggsano is a package developen by the R community within Sciensano to 
    implement available templates, colour schemes, and figures lay-out according to
    the Sciensano house style guide. The package includes colour schemes that could
    be integrated in ggplot2, and the package will take a ggplot2 object and recompile
    it according to the Sciensano house style.
